@base = https://endpoints.hckr.mx/puedopasar
@apiKey = {{$dotenv APP_KEY}}

# ──── DATA ────

### Get current status data (reads from status.json, falls back to static data)
GET {{base}}/data
x-dnn-apikey: {{apiKey}}

# ──── REFRESH ────

### Trigger orchestrator to refresh status (fire-and-forget, respects cooldown)
POST {{base}}/refresh
x-dnn-apikey: {{apiKey}}
